			 Set up Python Machine Learning Services (In-Database) 

					 
								 12/20/2017 
							 13 minutes to read 
							 
								 Contributors 
								 
											 
											 
											 
											 
								 

					 In this article 
						 THIS TOPIC APPLIES TO:   SQL Server (Windows only) Azure SQL Database Azure SQL Data Warehouse Parallel Data Warehouse    This article describes how to install the components required for Python by running the  SQL Server setup wizard, and following the interactive prompts. 
 Machine learning options in SQL Server setup 
 Choose the  Machine Learning Services  feature, and select  Python  as the language. 
 The  Shared Features  section contains a separate installation option,  Machine Learning Server (Standalone) . This option supports operationalization of Python code on a server that does not have SQL Ser